                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h4 class="card-title">Sarah’s Greenhouse Revolution</h4>
                                    <p><strong>Location:</strong> Kisumu County</p>
                                    <p>Sarah, a small-scale vegetable farmer, struggled with unpredictable rains and
                                        low yields. Through BLSP’s Smart Farming Initiative, she received training in
                                        climate-smart agriculture and access to a greenhouse and drip irrigation system.
                                    </p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Her vegetable yields increased by 50%, providing surplus for sale.</li>
                                        <li> Household income doubled, enabling her children to attend school regularly.
                                        </li>
                                        <li>Sarah now trains other women farmers in her community, spreading sustainable
                                            practices.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
