                                    <p><strong>Location:</strong> Machakos County</p>
                                    <p>Daniel, a young farmer, lacked access to modern agricultural tools. BLSP’s
                                        Agro-Innovation & Technology Initiative introduced him to solar irrigation and
                                        drone-assisted crop monitoring.</p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Reduced water usage by 40% while increasing crop quality.</li>
                                        <li>Daniel started a local drone service for nearby farms, creating jobs for two
